<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7701397>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Palaeorhoptrocentrus kanti gen. et sp. nov. (holotype, female, Baltic amber, BX 54/22) (A) Habitus, lateral view. (B) Body (head, mesosoma and metasoma), lateral view. (C) Head and basal antennomeres of antenna, lateral view. (D) Head and mesosoma, lateral view. (E) Propodeum, metasoma and ovipositor, lateral view. (F) Apical antennomeres of antenna. (G) Wings. (H) Medial part of fore wing." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7701397/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7701401>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Palaeorhoptrocentrus kanti gen. et sp. nov. (paratype, female, Baltic amber, BX 54/22) (A) Habitus, dorsal view. (B) Habitus, lateral view. (C) Head and mesosoma, dorsal view. (D) Head and mesosoma, lateral view. (E) Propodeum and basal half of metasoma, dorsal view. (F) Metasoma, dorsal view. (G) Metasoma and ovipositor, lateral view. (H) Fore wing." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7701401/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

